step.context:
\text{What can you say about elements of a matrix}\\
\text{whose elements satisfy $a_{ij}=a_{ji}$ and}\\
\text{$a_{ij}=-a_{ji}$.}

step.tex:
a_{ij}=a_{ji}=0\\
\text{A matrix with all elements that satisfy $a_{ij}=a_{ji}$}\\
\text{and $a_{ij}+a_{ji}=0$ is a zero matrix.}

a_{ij}=a_{ji}=0\\
\text{A matrix with all elements that satisfy $a_{ij}=a_{ji}$}\\
\text{and $a_{ij}+a_{ji}=0$ is a diagonal matrix.}
